# Project Overview

This is a Next.js CV/Portfolio application built with React and TypeScript. The project uses the App Router pattern introduced in Next.js 13+.

## Main Files and Directories
- [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx) - Root layout component
- [app/page.tsx](mdc:app/page.tsx) - Home page component
- [components/](mdc:components/) - Reusable UI components
- [data/](mdc:data/) - Data files for portfolio, profile, and other content
- [styles/](mdc:styles/) - SCSS styles
- [public/](mdc:public/) - Static assets
- [utils/](mdc:utils/) - Utility functions
- [store/](mdc:store/) - State management with Zustand

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 14
- React 18
- TypeScript
- SCSS
- Zustand for state management
- EmailJS for contact form
- React PDF for PDF generation
